description:
Deep within the ocean lurk strange creatures, venomous sea snakes, and electric eels. Can the Jellyfish escape these creatures? Will they ever reach the surface of the ocean? Without a new home, these Jellyfish may not survive much longer! It’s your job to bring these Jellyfish upwards. Bounce on rocky ledges and use Starfish as a boost. Collect golden coins to unlock new Jellyfish.

EXCITING FUN AND ITS FREE TO DOWNLOAD!!!

Challenge Your Friends for Highest Score!
Great Time-Killer Game!
